:1 沙發(sofa)
:3 躺椅(couch)
:3 桌(table)
:5 安樂椅(easy chair)
:6 梳妝台(dresser)
:6 搖椅(rocking chair)
:8 咖啡桌(coffee table)
:9 搖椅(rocker)
:10 情人座(love seat)
:11 衣櫃(chest of drawers)
:12 書桌(desk)
:13 床(bed)
...
:22 書櫃(bookcase)
:27 擺設櫃(cabinet)
:29 長凳(bench)
